    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >&quot;Same Brain&quot; is an exciting and interactive party game where participants must think alike to win. The game pits two contestants against each other in a battle of wits and hilarity as they try to match their answers with the other players. Each round features a variety of prompts and questions, and the goal is for team members to come up with the same or similar answers to score points.   Meant to be played online with friends via Zoom, Discord, or on the couch together at a party. </p>",
